AUDIO: 'Hi everyone. Today we\'re introducing Bible Studio, our most powerful product yet for 4K relighting running locally right on your desktop. These incredible results are all from Bble Studio running our most advanced video to PVR model'

[00:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Switch Site 3 directly on your machine. B Studio is available today and runs locally on high performance Windows machine equipped with Nvidia GPUs.'

[00:26] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Designed for professionals, Viv Studio unlocks the full potential of Switch Light 3 with true 4K processing, unlimited rendering, and 16bit EXR outputs. No uploads, no credits, just'

[00:40] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'results. Just drop in your footage and generate a complete set of PDR passes, normals, albido, roughness, specular, metallic, depth, and alpha. All packed into multi-'

[00:54] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'channelannel EXRs ready to go. Move seamlessly into your pipeline with our Blender and Unreal Engine plugins. No round trip headaches, just'

[01:06] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'relighting. Bring cinematic lighting to any shot with our built-in 3D editor featuring point lights, HDRIs, and real-time lighting controls. And because everything runs locally, your files'

[01:19] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'completely stay with you. Perfect for studios that demand speed, security, and full control. Biv Studio is available today. It\'s time to relight right on your desktop.'
